{"tid":1328751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解難民之父要幫政府、民建聯解圍？","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:45:35.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0f995ad987326ba071695c69d23692707195ec","tid":1328751,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"張超雄回應兩個重點<br />\n<br />\n1. 修改單次性移交逃犯條例，不包括大陸同澳門，變相可以引渡逃犯由香港至台灣，但台灣方面就唔可以引渡逃犯返香港。知道有政治犯同義士逃亡到台灣，條例係唔允許移送佢哋返來香港。<br />\n<br />\n2. 修改條例屬私人草案，如果發現到政府僭建任何東西，就算上到大會討論，佢都可以隨時撤回修例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8OnJeF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8OnJeF.png&h=1d87f739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1422203927/posts/10220527329719546?s=753094347&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1422203927%2Fposts%2F10220527329719546%3Fs%3D753094347%26sfns%3Dmo&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=e1addb3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1422203927/posts/10220527329719546?s=753094347&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"39c5bdab3f66ca342e1f6724a3b237e3efef0ead","tid":1328751,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"張超雄的初心是什麼並不重要，佢提出私人條例草案的客觀效果，就是為特區政府解圍，分散抗爭力量，擾亂示威方向。簡單說，佢的作用就是「搞散運動」。勸籲「泛民」中人說服佢撤回。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7b2f6a9b588621a716184283aac60498f92e0c","tid":1328751,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d52f48e24e61c9f1c56d934fe36a0f4ee5e320","tid":1328751,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"[quote]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【杜絕分化】熱狗惡行 24小時輪流廣播 （2）</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295085\